gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 129, Jazz 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors win their fifth straight game as they defeat the Jazz, 129-107. Klay Thompson put up 26 points (3-7 3pt. FG) and six rebounds for the Warriors, while Stephen Curry added 25 points (15 points, 5-7 3pt. FG in the 4th quarter), six rebounds and 10 assists in the victory. Jordan Clarkson tallied 22 points (4-7 3pt. FG) and four rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 26-25 on the season, while the Jazz fall to 26-28.
